01:24:37.050 --> 01:24:38.834
<i>Alabama dengan satu
jedah tersisa.</i>


1145
01:24:38.859 --> 01:24:40.328
<i>Rutledge memegang bola.</i>

1146
01:24:40.353 --> 01:24:43.357
<i>Melihat ke sisi tengah,
dan itu...</i>


1147
01:24:43.970 --> 01:24:45.972
<i>Tertangkap!
Touchdown!</i>


1148
01:24:47.410 --> 01:24:49.333
